==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polyspermy
<hw>Pol"y*sper`my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
<def>Fullness of sperm, or seed; the passage of more than one
spermatozoon into the vitellus in the impregnation of the
ovum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polysporous</ent>⟦br⟧
